My opinion? Let her wear the scarf, the school needs to use some common sence. If the rules forbid it, then amend the rules with a narrowly-tailored exception to religious headwear. <span style="font-weight: bold">However</span>, forbidding these scarves at school, while perhaps silly and being anal on the rules, is not unconstitutional.<span class="gensmall"></span>


